finger — List information about a user.
logname — Return a user's login name.
who — Report which users are logged in to the system.
-G, --groups---print all group IDs.

id -a: To print user name, UID of all the group to which the user belongs
id -G: To print all different group IDs (effective, real and supplementary)
id -g: To print the effective group ID
id -u: To print the effective user ID
